          <p class="pmeta">AWS cost optimization CLI with CSV export and an audit checklist for idle EC2, unattached EBS, unused EIPs, and untagged resources. Pairs well with cloud-native dashboards; automates on-the-ground fixes. CLI-first, CSV-friendly, and opinionated about what to fix next.</p>
